metadata.name: pretty fears #1/3
metadata.description:
"Pretty Fears" is a tribute to the power and beauty of vulnerability, captured in a fleeting moment. 
As the gentle rays of sunlight touch her bare skin, she gets lost in thought and emotion. A mix of pleasure and fear that evokes a sense of soulful mystery. Could it be the thrill and uncertainty of new love? The fear of losing it again? The beauty of the moment lies not only in her natural form but also in the complex web of emotions it weaves.

Ana Tomouanu in Cologne, Germany
